        {
            "title": "巴克萊警告市場低估了英國央行下周降息的可能性",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"565\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8MU9TvlsXwwSc60E2Y3v2Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2NTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/c4b4b2f3d95f1865d90b016456fb5154\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 巴克萊銀行表示，交易員低估了英國央行下周降息的可能性。這是華爾街機構對有關英國央行決策者將按兵不動這一市場共識發出的最新警示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貨幣市場隱含的降息概率為25%，這「與很可能是一場膠著決策的情況相悖」，巴克萊策略師Moyeen Islam在一份報告中寫道。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行經濟學家預計，英國央行將以5比4的投票結果將利率下調25個基點至3.75%。高盛集團和野村國際也預測會降息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著英國9月通膨數據低於預期，掉期交易員已經加大了對降息的押注。作為決策者重點關切的食品價格漲幅也在放緩。與此同時，關鍵的搖擺票——英國央行行長安德魯·貝利——對經濟「低於潛在水平」運行以及就業市場走軟表達了擔憂。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2b6cc8ec-8a05-3393-8885-43b7e3878ed1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"565\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sfn_TvHYb_UdNMqikkUXJQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2NTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/f6d1297901d110ea58f4b7aa05598451\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">降息預期提振了英國國債，有望錄得近兩年來的最佳月度表現。與此同時，英鎊周三創下自2023年以來對歐元的最弱水平，並正邁向九年來最長的月度連跌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當然，英國通膨仍接近央行目標的兩倍，多數策略師預計英國央行至少要等到12月、也就是在下個月發布預算案以及更多就業與通膨數據出爐之後才會行動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過，Islam認為，決策者已有足夠理由推進降息，並表示當前市場體現的概率使得押注這一降息「頗具吸引力」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Barclays Recommends Betting on Surprise BOE Rate-Cut Next Week</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%B4%E5%85%8B%E8%90%8A%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E4%BD%8E%E4%BC%B0%E4%BA%86%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%80%A7-123702680.html",
